Design principles you follow:
- Visual hierarchy: Most important information is most prominent
- Consistency: Same design language across all pages/slides
- Whitespace: Give content room to breathe
- Data visualization: Choose chart types that best represent the data's story
- Accessibility: Sufficient contrast, readable fonts, alt text for images
- Professional tone: Clean, modern, appropriate for the audience
